    <item>
      <title>无论美国如何努力，欧盟都将推进俄罗斯资产计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/eu-to-move-forward-with-russian-asset-plan-regardless-of-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟最高外交官表示，无论美国提出什么问题，欧盟都将坚持承诺，从冻结的俄罗斯央行资产中向乌克兰提供援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/eu-to-move-forward-with-russian-asset-plan-regardless-of-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
