    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡左翼候选人通过反腐运动取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/sri-lanka-leftist-candidate-akd-gains-ground-in-election-on-anti-corruption-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位有着斯里兰卡马克思主义社会主义政策根基的候选人在下个月的总统选举中获得了支持，他强烈要求打击腐败并仔细审查与中国的投资交易，以避免再次陷入债务陷阱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/sri-lanka-leftist-candidate-akd-gains-ground-in-election-on-anti-corruption-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 05:09:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国关键矿产计划获两党支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/us-sees-bipartisan-backing-for-africa-critical-minerals-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院一位高级官员向非洲各国政府保证，即使在政府更迭之后，通过发展非洲基础设施来帮助对抗中国影响力的举措仍将继续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/us-sees-bipartisan-backing-for-africa-critical-minerals-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 15:54:53 GMT</pubDate>
